intent.user_query: Which product has the most service tickets?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.ServiceTickets st ON p.ProductID = st.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY COUNT(st.TicketID) DESC LIMIT 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(st.TicketID) FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.ServiceTickets st ON p.ProductID = st.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY COUNT(st.TicketID) DESC LIMIT 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
